data.description: Prime location in District 2! This spacious home is over 3,000 square feet and located on 6.5 beautiful acres with pond barn and dog kennels! With a total of 4 bedrooms, 3 and a half baths, 2 owner suites, a formal Living room, Dining room, a den with wood burning fireplace and a sunroom, there is a space for everyone to spread out, relax and unwind! In addition to the home's attached garage, you'll also find this home offers plenty of space for storage and parking for farm and recreational equipment, in the 2 car detached garage. This space would make a great workshop as well for the hobbyist. This home truly has it all.  Sellers would like to sell as is. Listing agent is offering a $1,500 bonus to the agent who gets this home sold by the end of January. Additional land with pond view offers power, tennis courts and a covered bbq patio!
